import sys
input = sys.stdin.readline
t = int(input())
for _ in range(t):
    n = int(input())
    word = input()
    word_syllables = ''
    i = 0
    while i < n:
        if n - i == 2:
            word_syllables += word[i] + word[i + 1]
            break
        if n - i == 3:
            word_syllables += word[i] + word[i + 1] + word[i + 2]
            break
        if word[i + 3] == 'a' or word[i + 3] == 'e':
            word_syllables += word[i] + word[i + 1] + '.'
            i += 2
        else:
            word_syllables += word[i] + word[i + 1] + word[i + 2] + '.'
            i += 3
    print(word_syllables)
